@Gestion.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5284

### 1. Verificar si tu API generˇ el mapa OpenAPI (Swagger base) correctamente:
GET {{Gestion.API_HostAddress}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

### 2. Testear tu controlador creando un Gasto:
POST {{Gestion.API_HostAddress}}/api/Gastos
Content-Type: application/json

